11
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,239
You have Anxiety Disorder.

12
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,480
I know.

13
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,719
Yesterday, I... I gave...

14
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:55,760
Don't say a word.

15
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,200
Pei Xi.

16
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,200
Come here, come here.

17
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:05,159
Coming.

18
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:51,599
Are we ready to begin?

19
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:52,919
Yes, we can begin.

20
00:02:53,439 --> 00:02:55,560
Patient's Blood pressure 120/60.

21
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,560
