39
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,960
Yes.

40
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,960
Dr. Jiang, thank you so much.

41
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,159
Thank goodness you were here today.

42
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,520
