43
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:08,879
It's settled then.

44
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,039
Vice President Qin, join us.

45
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,800
Doctor.

46
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,560
Thank you so much.

47
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,280
I...

48
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,400
