49
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,800
How is she?

50
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,399
Didn't you see her?

51
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,040
I'll go check.

52
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,759
Why are you hitting him?!

53
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:21,879
Dr. Jiang, are you okay?

54
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:22,959
Rich people's lives matter,

55
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,680
