56
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,399
Have you lost your mind?

57
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,920
Call the police, now!

58
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,319
Where's your conscience?

59
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:33,279
You knew my daughter's condition best.

60
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,759
My daughter got here before his son.

61
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,920
Why did you ignore my daughter

62
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:40,519
