63
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,399
Doctor.

64
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,600
I'm begging you.

65
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:48,000
She's my only daughter.

66
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,800
If you save my daughter,

67
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,120
