68
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:56,079
Doctor, save my daughter!

69
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,040
Save my daughter!

70
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:58,800
Sir.

71
00:04:58,839 --> 00:04:59,480
What are you doing?

72
00:04:59,759 --> 00:05:00,399
What do you think you're doing?

73
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,680
- Save my daughter! - Sir.

74
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,079
- Save my daughter! - This guy...

75
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,000
- Save my daughter! - Calm down first.

76
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,399
Let go!

77
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:13,839
Doctor.

78
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,439
I'm begging you.

79
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:22,079
Unscrupulous Doctor Assaults Patient's Family in Public

80
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:24,079
What is wrong with our society?

81
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,519
At Pingjin First Hospital,

82
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:28,160
Attending Physician Jiang Tiancai of the Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Department,

83
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,759
