85
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:34,399
Why have ERs become conflict hotspots?

86
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,120
Is it a lack of communication,

87
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:38,040
or the strain on medical resources?

88
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:40,879
Looking at recent events at Pingjin First Hospital...

89
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:47,560
Why did you hit him?

90
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,199
He's a patient's family member.

91
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:53,680
You're a doctor.

92
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:55,720
Do you see this?

93
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,319
The heart of a healer.

94
00:05:58,519 --> 00:06:00,240
