98
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,079
You...

99
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,040
Look, just look at this.

100
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,759
The video shows it clear as day.

101
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:10,839
And you're still making excuses?

102
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,279
You must

103
00:06:15,639 --> 00:06:16,560
