125
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:29,519
Jiang Tiancai, listen to me.

126
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:31,240
I'm giving you two choices.

127
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,759
Either apologize publicly,

128
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,600
or be suspended.

129
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:43,079
The Golden Scalpel Award evaluations are about to start.

130
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,959
Don't you dare cause me trouble right now.

131
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:51,040
The Specialty Reputation Ranking is about to start.

132
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:55,319
Don't you dare cause me trouble right now.

133
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:02,079
